<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <title>Title</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no" />

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <style>
        hr {
            margin: 0.4rem 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: sans-serif;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <main>
        <div style="max-width: 1000px; margin:auto; gap:18px;" class="d-flex flex-column box pt-5">
            {{#each blog}}
            <img src="/images/{{banner}}" alt="" height="500px">
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                <div>
                    <h1 class="fw-5">{{title}}</h1>
                    <h6 style="color:#808e8a;">CreatedAt / {{createdAt}}</h6>
                </div>
                {{#if showedit}}
                <div>
                    <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/blog/edit/{{_id}}">Edit</a>
                    <!-- Button trigger modal -->
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#exampleModal">
                        Delete
                    </button>

                    <!-- Modal -->
                    <div class="modal fade" id="exampleModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel"
                        aria-hidden="true">
                        <div class="modal-dialog">
                            <div class="modal-content">
                                <div class="modal-header">
                                    <h1 class="modal-title fs-3
                                     fw-4 " id="exampleModalLabel">{{title}}</h1>
                                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"
                                        aria-label="Close"></button>
                                </div>
                                <div class="modal-body fs-5 fw-4 text-danger">
                                    Are u Sure u Want to Delete This Blog ?
                                </div>
                                <div class="modal-footer">
                                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary"
                                        data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                                    <a href="/blog/delete/{{_id}}"  class="btn btn-danger">Delete</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {{else}}
                <h6 style="color:#808e8a;">Written by {{author.name}}</h6>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            <hr>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Nemo totam cumque eveniet a dolorem eligendi qui
                dolores velit fuga eum unde deserunt, cum minus, ipsa ab mollitia architecto sunt aspernatur corporis!
                Laboriosam error fugiat sit molestias ipsa quae qui neque exercitationem quibusdam dolore aut magni
                debitis eos quam, enim doloremque.</p>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Ipsam officia rem velit provident dolor sint sed
                iure soluta? Esse quidem cumque natus, iusto vero aspernatur ex, maiores quam autem consequatur
                laudantium a unde libero, doloremque vel fugit! Veniam, iste adipisci tempore laborum voluptatum,
                recusandae quas placeat dolorem dignissimos, reprehenderit explicabo. Accusantium deleniti et ea nisi
                totam vel tenetur, blanditiis a, sit hic voluptatum est, quod ex necessitatibus atque! Fugiat sapiente
                aliquam alias! Possimus voluptatum, expedita soluta nihil doloremque magni laboriosam.</p>
            {{/each}}
        </div>
    </main>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.8/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-I7E8VVD/ismYTF4hNIPjVp/Zjvgyol6VFvRkX/vR+Vc4jQkC+hVqc2pM8ODewa9r"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-BBtl+eGJRgqQAUMxJ7pMwbEyER4l1g+O15P+16Ep7Q9Q+zqX6gSbd85u4mG4QzX+"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>